#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Wow !
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : Yeah , it 's really exciting .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) When is that ?
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : We go in June .
#Text=But next month we 're going to launch a big fund raising campaign to get together all the money to do it all .
#Text=But yeah , it 's pretty cool .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Are you still with the basketball ?
#Text=Are you going to continue with that ?
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : Yep ! I do !
#Text=So two weeks , no less than two weeks , the fourteenth of January , we go to the AIS for our first training camp of the Rio campaign .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) So I might be able to catch you guys again there .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : From the fourteenth to the seventeenth .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) It must have been disappointing in London — Let me put it like this :
#Text=I 'm watching the game , and it 's " oh no , they 're losing " but you do n't look like you 're losing .
#Text=You look like you 're having the time of your life .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : Yeah ! Definitely .
#Text=I mean , what we play for is to play on the world stage and it is a lot of fun .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Did you see how many people were there was ?
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : Yeah , it was insane .
#Text=In-sane .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) I was staring up at the top and I could not see the top rows .
#Text=They were completely in darkness .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : There was so many people there , and they were all supporting us .
#Text=It was so much fun .
#Text=It was the best I 've ever done .
#Text=But yeah , of course it 's disappointing , because you do n't want to win silver , or lose gold , but ...
#Text=( ( WN ) ) The silver 's pretty good !
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : Yeah , being second in the world 's pretty good , definitely , but silver 's tough .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) It 's just that the Gliders have never won .
#Text=They 've never won the World Championship , they 've never won at the Paralympics .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : We 've never won .
#Text=Yeah , so obviously we wanted to change that .
#Text=So yeah , definitely disappointing .
#Text=We did what we were capable of .
#Text=It was n't like we underperformed .
#Text=We did n't play badly .
#Text=We just were n't quite good enough .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Yeah .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : And the Germans were very good .
#Text=They worked really hard .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Really good .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin :
#Text=They were very good , so ...
#Text=( ( WN ) ) You played pretty well .
#Text=Shelley Chaplin : We had patches where we did n't play well , but that 's basketball .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) The whole team needed to find something and lift , because like ... we interviewed one of your team mates , and she we ca n't expect to win if we 're shooting 39 per cent .
#Text=Then of course you went ahead and won two games shooting 39 per cent , which sort of made a bit of a liar out of her ...
